==Paragraph Styles==
You can use spacing and headings to separate and organize paragraphs. Spacing between paragraphs make the text more readable, while headings provide visual cues that help users understand the structure of the article. Other styles, such as boxes and lists, make information easier to understand and remember.{br}

To increase spacing between paragraphs when you&rsquo;re editing, insert two line breaks in the wiki text. Single line breaks are ignored. {br}

The table below includes the paragraph styles you can use in wiki articles. ((({S:Hint}All the paragraph styles listed below should be used at the beginning of the line. 
